<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10150152>
    dc:description "FIGURES 49–52. Trichophthalma barbarossa Bigot, 1857: (49) feed on Francoa appendiculata A. Juss. ex Cav. (photo by Claudio Maureira) and (50) (photo by Fanny Araya) Trichophthalma commutata (Philippi, 1865): (51) feed on F. appendiculata (photo by Fanny Araya) and (52) resting in a wheel (photo by Pía Fernández)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10150152/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10150154>
    dc:description "FIGURE 53. Distribution map of Trichophthalma amaena Bigot, 1881 (green circles), Trichophthalma andina (Philippi, 1862) (Philippi, 1865) (red circles), Trichophthalma barbarossa Bigot, 1857 (orange circles), and Trichophthalma commutata (Philippi, 1865) (yellow circles)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10150154/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

